(953, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>1.	Developments in the business during the period;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(954, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>2.	Changes in key personnel, including management and shareholders;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(955, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>3.	Changes or new accounting systems put in place (including internal controls);</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(956, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>4.	New or changes to accounting policies and estimation techniques, including accounting estimates (including those that arise as a result of the first application of a new or revised accounting standard);</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(957, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>5.	New law or regulations applying to the business or changes in existing legislation;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(958, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>6.	Any known instances of non-compliance with law and regulations during the accounting period by the client or service organisation;</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(959, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>7.	Any instances of claims or litigation against the client during the accounting period  <i>(it is suggested that copies of invoices from legal advisers are requested to enable the audit team to decide whether or not third party confirmations are to be requested);</i></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(960, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>8.	Potential areas of significant risk in the business (including whether the client has a risk assessment process, either formal or ad-hoc, and any adverse matters the risk assessment process has identified during the accounting period)   <i>NB: PSA 240 paragraph 31 states that management override represents a significant risk in all entities. In addition, consideration should be given to the risk of fraud in revenue recognition;</i></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(961, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>9.	All entities are susceptible to fraud. Document any concerns or knowledge of fraud at the client or service organisation and where these might occur within the business    <i>(unless all of those charged with governance are involved in managing the entity, this should be specifically raised with both those charged with governance and management to corroborate the responses given);</i></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(962, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>10.	Communication (if any) to employees regarding views on business practices and ethical behaviour;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(963, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>11.	Use of journals and suspense accounts by the client;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
(964, 4, 'AC4', 'ac4sod', '<p>12.	Which figures in the primary statements are of most concern to the client (i.e. the ones that the client views as “material”), and what fluctuation to these figures would affect their view on the financial statements;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Active', NULL, '2024-04-02 12:47:31', NULL),
